title: The Secret Society of the Mad Hatters Patron Preview #14: Chad and JT Go To City Hall
description: Check out this sneak preview of the latest Tin Foil Hat Secret Society of the Mad Hatter Sneak Ep 14.  Sam and Ryan welcome Chad and JT to the show to talk about their brave fight against City Hall to save your right to House Party!!!
